message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which is tailored to meet your specific needs. Given its value and quality, we believe it's worth more than $120 to you. Considering its true worth and your satisfaction, I propose a price of $140 for the product. This price reflects the excellent value it offers and ensures that you receive a great deal while also allowing us to fairly compensate for our efforts and resources. I trust this proposal aligns with your expectations and would appreciate your consideration.
